Title: Nostalgic Nomad
DateModified: '2019-02-05'
DatePublished: '2019-02-05'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/nostalgic-nomad
SetInCountry: Zimbabwe
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Ene Agamah
AuthorCountry: United Kingdom (Great Britain
Text: This story is about a young girl that is desperately searching for the joy and
  innocence she once posessed as a child. Being plunged into the great big world and
  being forced to grow up before she was able to enjoy her childhood. She searches
  for the feelings and places she once loved an called home in hopes of finding that
  feeling of nostalgia. But along her journey she encounters many types of people
  and settings that teach her plenty lessons and opens her eyes to the beauty of the
  present.
